<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About BloodSend</title>
    <style>
        /* General Styles */
body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

.header {
    background-color: #e63946;
    color: white;
    padding: 15px 20px;
    text-align: center;
}

.logo {
    font-size: 24px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: white;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 20px auto;
    padding: 20px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

.about-section,
.mission-section,
.team-section {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}

.about-section h1,
.mission-section h2,
.team-section h2 {
    color: #e63946;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #555;
}


/* Responsive Design */
@media (max-width: 600px) {
    .content {
        padding: 15px;
    }

    .header {
        font-size: 20px;
    }

    p {
        font-size: 14px;
    }
}

    </style>

</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <a class="logo" href="/">BloodSend</a>
    </header>
    <main class="content">
        <section class="about-section">
            <h1>About BloodSend</h1>
            <p>
                BloodSend is a platform dedicated to connecting blood donors and recipients in need. 
                Our mission is to simplify the process of finding compatible donors and providing a 
                life-saving resource for those in critical conditions.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section class="mission-section">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
                To create a community-driven network where individuals can easily access and provide blood donations, 
                ensuring timely help to save lives.
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>